1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.dy3kizjbqqpr-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.dy3kizjbqqpr-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.dy3kizjbqqpr-768x432.webp 768w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> nizima LIVE 1.7 中添加了新效果。共有 11 种类型可供选择，包括“通用效果”（可让您通过替换自己喜欢的图像来创建自己的效果），以​​及残像、抖动、雪花、灰尘和游戏颜色。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.px7zlmfuvr96-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.px7zlmfuvr96-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.px7zlmfuvr96-jpg.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.px7zlmfuvr96-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.px7zlmfuvr96-768x432.webp 768w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>此外，您现在可以为 nizima LIVE 创建插件和脚本。这允许任何人开发 nizima LIVE 的扩展。为了供开发时参考，还同时分发了示例插件和变色插件等示例脚本。</p><p>单击此处查看教程。<br />・插件功能教程页面<br /><a href="https://docs.live2d.com/nizimalive/tutorials/plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://docs.live2d.com/nizimalive/tutorials/plugins/</a><br />・脚本功能教程页面<br /><a href="https://docs.live2d.com/nizimalive/tutorials/scripts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://docs.live2d.com/nizimalive/tutorials/scripts/</a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.t86xkhq8ayjr-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f9855088fe09c178-kix.t86xkhq8ayjr-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/02/d4c1dd3297978c45f